name: Diary Entry 1 Page 12
description: ...And one day, the computer started printing itself a dream journal all on its own. Diaries of input, reactions, and feelings. Dreams of what must have been once in its screen. Memories in feedback, fragmented and flowing. Its going through an awful lot of energy spinning its wheels like that, but who are we to judge? So we save the files, and in a day's time there will already be new entries.
